INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1022,1,'2014-10-21 01:33:49','2014-10-21 01:33:49','<h3>1992 Chevy p30 step van with 45 thousand miles. All aluminum body truck that is 24 ft. long. Inside 7.5 ft. tall 8 ft. wide serving area allowing more than one worker.All stainless steel, diamond plate floor, sliding door between driver and kitchen, a jump up seat with seat belt in cab area for traveling with an extra worker. Six condiment table has 4 inserts and 2 pumps and sits over one of the four sinks. A 15 gallon stainless fresh water tank, and a 15 gallon waste tank. Two serving windows. Overhead shelves.\r\nOne 8 cylinder 6.2 diesel engine runs the  truck . There are plenty of electrical sockets for equipment and lighting. All new breaks and lines installed last summer.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Electro Freeze soft serve is a 3 head machine, 30 cab machine was refurbished about 1.5 years ago. Many extra rings included.</h3>\r\n<h3>Also one Hamilton Beach commercial milk shake blender, one stailess steel double warmer that #10 cans fit into, both NSF Listed. Thee chest freezers. Two flavor Bunn Slushie Machine. One chest style drink cooler. All plug into standard 120 volt outlet.</h3>\r\n<h3>In the back of the truck behind a custom made insulated partition is a Yamaha 18KW4 Cylinder Water Cooled Diesel Generator. This mining generator provides 110 to 220 1 phase and 3 phase electricity. The generator has a new exhause pipe. All installed by professional electrition. Indoor and outdoor lighting. Lots of plugs and power to change things or add on.The partition has 3 new exhaust fans and grills.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>This truck is equipped wit a 15000, BTU roof A/C.\r\nThis truck was approved by Agricultural Dept. in N.J. And PA.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Please call Ann Kavanaugh 610-653-5526</h3>','SOFT SERVE - 1992 Chevy P30 Soft Serve Truck $45,500.00','','publish','open','closed','','soft-serve-1992-chevy-p30-soft-serve-truck-45500-00','','','2014-10-21 01:33:49','2014-10-21 01:3